{"tid":126993,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(睇書撚)全港邊間圖書館環境最啱打書釘?","createTime":"2017-02-19T18:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T03:27:25.000Z","uid":44807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"979265d83c19f72d23ec078081e1c7b1861b79ed","tid":126993,"uid":44807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:18:50.000Z","msg":"估唔到咁多連登仔鍾意睇書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁多位巴打有無去圖書館打書釘習慣，我一去可以去8粒鐘坐足成日，各位有無覺得邊間圖書館去過覺得環境正，藏書多，細路MK廢老最少，而又啱靜靜地睇書?<br />\n<br />\n個人幾鍾意大會堂，雖然係要上上落落，座位比較少，但近海皮始終較偏僻，出入d人都有教養d。沙田都okay，藏書量夠多，但出入人多，次次我都會走入參考圖書館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1e941d76510d87d194d9330f9c5b7672ece09a","tid":126993,"uid":75674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:19:28.000Z","msg":"圖書館啲書好垃圾"},{"pid":"28fc4f9dc5ab457c0fc83fed19ecb554672ec39c","tid":126993,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖書館啲書好垃圾</blockquote><br />\n掂完隻手過多陣會痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac5bd832ee6af76d221bd1444ab4cd545300b12","tid":126993,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:21:08.000Z","msg":"駱克道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d3d5f6b6b0c8aecd107f4f39c18ec71a04cd18","tid":126993,"uid":42002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"屏山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夠大"},{"pid":"a200f52f90478ac64b23b1be7bd83d1ed67ab2d2","tid":126993,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>圖書館啲書好垃圾</blockquote><br />\n掂完隻手過多陣會痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前搭巴士朝朝見個阿嬸一路撩鼻屎一路睇書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />